Package makesudokus.logic.algorithms.crook

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    A data container class for a single Sudoku Cell used by the Crook's algorithm solver.
    CrookSolver
    Class for solving a sudoku J.F.Crook style.
    PreemptiveSet
    A preemptive set is a tuple of small lists shaped like {[1,2,6], [c(1,7), c(1,9), c(2,9)]} (example from Crook's paper.
    PreemptiveSetExaminer  
    SudokuBoard
    A container class for all of the cells.
